@startuml Hello Pages - Sequence Diagram
title Hello Pages — Frontend / Backend Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "React Frontend\n(Amplify)" as Frontend
participant "Express Backend\n(App Runner)" as Backend

== Page Load ==

Frontend -> Backend: GET /api/pages
Backend --> Frontend: 200 OK — []
Frontend -> Frontend: Render empty page list

== Save a Page (happy path) ==

User -> Frontend: Types text and clicks Save
Frontend -> Frontend: Disable Save button\n(loading = true)
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/pages\n{ "text": "..." }
Backend -> Backend: Create page object\n{ id, text, createdAt }
Backend --> Frontend: 201 Created\n{ id, text, createdAt }
Frontend -> Frontend: Prepend new page to list\nClear text input\nEnable Save button\n(loading = false)
Frontend --> User: Updated list displayed

== Save a Page (timeout / backend unreachable) ==

User -> Frontend: Types text and clicks Save
Frontend -> Frontend: Disable Save button\n(loading = true)
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/pages\n{ "text": "..." }
note right of Frontend: AbortController cancels\nthe request after 8 seconds
Frontend -> Frontend: Enable Save button\n(loading = false)
Frontend --> User: "Unable to save the page." error shown

@enduml
